OL,3,CEx council worker and roofer jailed
OL,4,Cfor scamming authority out of #88,000
OL,6,FA former council worker has been
OL,7,Fjailed, alongside a roofer - for
OL,8,Fscamming New Forest District Council
OL,9,Fout of more than #88,000.
OL,11,FSouthampton Crown Court heard that ex-
OL,12,Fcouncil maintenance operative Richard
OL,13,FCullen, 55, from Luton, received
OL,14,Fbribes from 34-year-old Mark Diaper,
OL,15,Fwho worked at a roofing company in
OL,16,FSouthampton which is now no longer
OL,17,Ftrading, to secure work which was then
OL,18,Fovercharged.
