OL,3,CEx council worker and roofer jailed
OL,4,Cfor scamming authority out of #88,000
OL,6,FCullen referred maintenance jobs to
OL,7,Fthe roofing firm for a 10% cut in any
OL,8,Fprofit.
OL,10,FJobs above #15,000 had to go out to
OL,11,Ftender and on occasion he asked Diaper
OL,12,Fto split a quotation into two so it
OL,13,Fdid not look so big.
OL,15,FHe also encouraged him to add
OL,16,Fexpensive elements like scaffolding to
OL,17,Finvoices to push up profits.
OL,19,FIn January 2019, council managers
OL,20,Fnoticed that spend authorised by
OL,21,FCullen had increased by 146%.
