OL,6,FSoon after, Cullen was found asleep at
OL,7,Fhis desk - he was suspended and
OL,8,Fsubsequently dismissed.
OL,10,FMessages between the men were
OL,11,Funcovered as part of the case by New
OL,12,FForest District Council.
OL,14,FThese showed Cullen kept Diaper
OL,15,Finformed of jobs, with Diaper
OL,16,Fresponding 'my man keep them coming
OL,17,Fbud let's get the money in the bank'.
OL,18,FIn September 2018, Cullen asked how
OL,19,Fmuch 'roofing dollar' he was likely to
OL,20,Fhave coming his way.
