OL,6,FBy February 2019 it was dawning on the
OL,7,Fmen that they may be in trouble, with
OL,8,FCullen remarking to Diaper that he is
OL,9,F"Gonna wipe my phone tonight got a
OL,10,Fprogram that overwrites so nothing can
OL,11,Fbe recovered...I'll pop over and do
OL,12,Fyours if you like?"
OL,14,FCullen was jailed for 58 months
OL,15,Fimprisonment and Diaper for 32 months
OL,16,Fimprisonment at Southampton Crown
OL,17,FCourt.
